Package ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol.model

Class PropertyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol.model.PropertyInfo

  • public class PropertyInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes vehicle signal property information.

    The information includes the path, node type, data type, value, property ID, and zone ID of the vehicle signal property, as well as whether the property value can be set.

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Ivi.VehicleControl
